They grow by the day.

560
01:12:40,204 --> 01:12:44,675
Benigno, I am thinking of taking
a trip... I have to work.

561
01:12:45,124 --> 01:12:47,160
And Lydia?

562
01:12:47,684 --> 01:12:50,072
She doesn't need me anymore.

563
01:12:52,003 --> 01:12:53,994
Did you break up?

564
01:12:54,923 --> 01:12:57,843
You can call it that way.

565
01:12:57,843 --> 01:13:01,801
I expected this, Marco.
Don't ask why, I just did.

566
01:13:03,322 --> 01:13:07,838
There was something in your
relationship that didn't function right.

567
01:13:08,162 --> 01:13:10,201
When are you going?

568
01:13:10,201 --> 01:13:13,079
Soon, but I'll see you before
