569
01:13:13,361 --> 01:13:15,716
I am so sorry you are going.

570
01:13:20,481 --> 01:13:23,438
I am leaving, Benigno.
I'll see you soon.

571
01:13:25,720 --> 01:13:29,269
She didn't have her period yet?

572
01:13:30,720 --> 01:13:34,678
I am looking at the month's report.
She should have had it.

573
01:13:35,999 --> 01:13:38,354
Yes, it's a bit late.

574
01:13:50,118 --> 01:13:53,996
Two weeks. That's a lot.
Are you sure she had it last month?

575
01:13:54,637 --> 01:13:58,755
I personally dealt with it.
It was when you had the flu.

576
01:13:59,917 --> 01:14:02,192
