doesn't have a period anymore.

579
01:14:08,796 --> 01:14:12,391
Anyway, we should tell Dr Vega.

580
01:14:30,234 --> 01:14:33,829
I brought some of my guides
for Alicia and you.

581
01:14:35,514 --> 01:14:37,822
I said goodbye to Lydia.

582
01:14:39,353 --> 01:14:43,551
