didn't let me enter the room.

583
01:14:45,473 --> 01:14:47,622
Is there something wrong?

584
01:14:48,032 --> 01:14:50,990
No. Just some infection
that Alicia got.

585
01:14:51,192 --> 01:14:54,152
Can you drive me home?
I am done with work.

586
01:14:54,152 --> 01:14:57,232
-It's not serious, I hope.
-I don't know.

587
01:14:57,232 --> 01:15:01,144
They do some medical exams,
but they haven't told me anything.

588
01:15:02,151 --> 01:15:05,191
Brazil...

589
01:15:05,191 --> 01:15:07,421
...Turkey, Cuba.

590
01:15:08,271 --> 01:15:11,342
-I will read them to Alicia.
-They are guides.

591
01:15:11,790 --> 01:15:14,630
Yours. They must be good.

592
01:15:14,630 --> 01:15:17,144
-Are you travelling alone?
-Yes.

593
01:15:17,430 --> 01:15:20,466
I would like to talk to you
about this before you go.

594
01:15:20,789 --> 01:15:23,940
-About what?
-loneliness.

595
01:15:24,109 --> 01:15:26,384
I want to get married.

596
01:15:28,909 --> 01:15:31,948
-Alicia, of course!
-Benigno, you are nuts!

597
01:15:31,948 --> 01:15:34,988
We will get along better than
most couples.

598
01:15:34,988 --> 01:15:38,219
-Why shouldn't I marry her?
-Because she is in a coma!

599
01:15:39,908 --> 01:15:43,456
Because she can't say 'yes'
in the church!

600
01:15:43,867 --> 01:15:47,427
Because, she is virtually dead!

601
01:15:47,427 --> 01:15:49,267
Get in the car!

602
01:15:49,267 --> 01:15:51,700
-What are you talking about?
-Get in the car!

603
01:15:57,706 --> 01:16:01,142
Your relationship with Alicia
is a crazy monologue!

604
01:16:01,426 --> 01:16:04,940
We often talk to PVS,
but we don't marry them.

605
01:16:05,505 --> 01:16:09,339
Incredible what you are saying.
I had a different opinion of you.

606
01:16:09,625 --> 01:16:13,140
Don't say or think about it
ever again!

607
01:16:13,704 --> 01:16:18,300
Promise!...If you say that to
anyone else, you will be in trouble!

608
01:16:20,384 --> 01:16:23,342
If that calms you down,
then I promise.

609
01:16:23,584 --> 01:16:26,623
-Regardless of how much you like her...
-You like her too, right?

610
01:16:26,623 --> 01:16:28,693
Of course I like her.

611
01:16:29,263 --> 01:16:32,943
-She likes you too.
-She is virtually dead!

612
01:16:32,943 --> 01:16:36,822
She has no feelings about me,
you, or herself!

613
01:16:36,822 --> 01:16:39,336
Understand that!

614
01:16:44,342 --> 01:16:48,141
Our patient Alicia Roncero
was raped and is pregnant.

615
01:16:48,141 --> 01:16:51,421
Before I tell her father
I want you to tell me...

616
01:16:51,421 --> 01:16:54,461
...which bastard did it!

617
01:16:54,461 --> 01:16:56,820
Everyone is upset.

618
01:16:56,820 --> 01:17:00,529
You are responsible. Alicia
was on your floor.

619
01:17:00,780 --> 01:17:03,931
Then allow me to explain the
situation.

620
01:17:04,540 --> 01:17:06,735
Rosa, please.

621
01:17:07,899 --> 01:17:11,653
Alicia's period stopped
two months ago.

622
01:17:12,019 --> 01:17:16,012
I thought it was one month
initially, but I was wrong.

623
01:17:16,219 --> 01:17:19,255
