625
01:17:22,698 --> 01:17:25,895
I was down with flu
during that week.

626
01:17:26,858 --> 01:17:29,815
You wrote that.
Right, Benigno?

627
01:17:30,057 --> 01:17:33,094
-It is your typewriting.
-Yes, it was me.

628
01:17:33,297 --> 01:17:36,130
Why did you lie?

629
01:17:36,657 --> 01:17:39,097
I didn't want it to become a problem.

630
01:17:39,097 --> 01:17:42,532
On other occasions, the patients'
periods have also stopped.

631
01:17:43,776 --> 01:17:47,735
How come no one noticed?
Where is the night person?

632
01:17:47,936 --> 01:17:51,132
She can't come today.
She phoned.

633
01:17:51,215 --> 01:17:53,375
Didn't see notice anything strange?

634
01:17:53,375 --> 01:17:57,607
She has problems at home.
A lot of nights she doesn't come.

635
01:17:57,815 --> 01:18:00,375
And who replaces her?

636
01:18:03,894 --> 01:18:06,966
I will tell Roncero
that his daughter...

637
01:18:07,294 --> 01:18:10,092
