a nutter?

638
01:18:10,174 --> 01:18:12,368
Lets calm down for a bit.

639
01:18:13,973 --> 01:18:19,047
Benigno, do you realise you
are the prime suspect?

640
01:18:19,893 --> 01:18:22,972
Why did you hide the first delay?

641
01:18:22,972 --> 01:18:27,170
What explanation do you have?
Would you ever harm Alicia?

642
01:18:27,412 --> 01:18:29,323
Definitely not!

643
01:18:34,691 --> 01:18:37,451
Last night I was
at the parkin lot...

644
01:18:37,451 --> 01:18:41,285
...and overheard a discussion
between Benigno and Marco.

645
01:18:41,371 --> 01:18:44,760
Benigno said he wanted to
marry Alicia.

646
01:18:45,130 --> 01:18:48,964
Marco tried to change his mind,
but in vain.

647
01:18:51,730 --> 01:18:54,090
Lots of couples, he said...

648
01:18:54,090 --> 01:18:57,445
...don'r get along
as well as him and Alicia.

649
