653
01:19:35,006 --> 01:19:37,076
He doesn't work here anymore.

654
01:19:38,165 --> 01:19:40,395
-Are you sure?
-Positive.

655
01:19:40,765 --> 01:19:43,245
-And sister Rosa Lazaga;
-Who are you?

656
01:19:43,245 --> 01:19:45,805
-Marco Zuloaga.
-I will put you through.

657
