679
01:22:19,061 --> 01:22:22,291
-Are you a relative?
-A friend.

680
01:22:22,420 --> 01:22:26,095
-Marco Zuloaga is my name.
-Can I see your I.D.?

681
01:22:28,860 --> 01:22:32,647
-Can I call him?
-He will call you.

682
01:22:32,939 --> 01:22:36,409
