and Sunday.

685
01:22:50,978 --> 01:22:54,765
But the lodger should ask for
the visit.

686
01:22:55,057 --> 01:22:58,174
If he doesn't want to see you,
there is nothing we can do.

687
01:22:59,657 --> 01:23:03,615
And something else. We don't
have prisoners here...

688
01:23:04,616 --> 01:23:08,894
We don't have prisoners here,
we have lodgers.

689
01:23:44,333 --> 01:23:46,607
Marco, is that you?

690
01:23:47,492 --> 01:23:51,690
I am glad to hear your voice.
I asked your visit on Saturday.

691
01:23:54,052 --> 01:23:56,281
-Where are you?
-Outside the clinique.

692
01:23:58,371 --> 01:24:02,284
