I can pay him.

720
01:25:58,720 --> 01:26:01,760
I will rent it.
I am currently homeless.

721
01:26:01,760 --> 01:26:05,036
Great. I am glad you will be
my tenant.

722
01:26:05,799 --> 01:26:09,712
I was thinking about you a lot,
especially during the nights.

723
01:26:10,479 --> 01:26:13,835
-Why during the nights?
-Because I study during the nights.

724
01:26:14,079 --> 01:26:16,751
I read all your guides.

725
01:26:16,918 --> 01:26:20,478
Like travelling with you
next to me...

726
01:26:20,478 --> 01:26:22,867
...telling me things.

727
01:26:23,158 --> 01:26:26,195
I liked Avan's the most.

728
01:26:26,438 --> 01:26:28,667
I became one with those people...

729
01:26:28,757 --> 01:26:31,794
...that have nothing
and invent everything.

730
01:26:32,757 --> 01:26:35,917
And you describing
the Cuban girl...

731
01:26:35,917 --> 01:26:38,836
...in front of her window
by the sea...

732
01:26:38,836 --> 01:26:40,872
...waiting in vain...

733
01:26:41,356 --> 01:26:44,428
...for something that will
never happen.

734
01:26:45,036 --> 01:26:47,994
I was thinking that woman is me.

735
01:27:05,994 --> 01:27:09,145
Good morning. I am Benigno's
friend.

736
01:27:09,674 --> 01:27:12,392
You are Marco, the Argentinian?

737
01:27:12,753 --> 01:27:17,383
Benigno called me.
Will you take his appartment?

738
01:27:18,193 --> 01:27:22,424
It will be dirty. He wouldn't
let me in to clean it.

739
01:27:23,872 --> 01:27:27,831
-And I didn't want any money...
-It's OK, I will take care of it.

740
01:27:28,112 --> 01:27:31,740
Shall I give you the key?...
I will go look for it...

741
01:27:38,231 --> 01:27:40,222
Did you see him?

742
01:27:41,311 --> 01:27:44,063
-How is he?
-Well.

743
01:27:45,270 --> 01:27:49,190
Poor guy, he wasn't even lucky
during his imprisonment.

744
01:27:49,190 --> 01:27:51,390
No publicity!

745
01:27:51,390 --> 01:27:55,507
No TV, no reporters.
No one came here.

746
01:27:55,989 --> 01:27:59,149
They didn't condescend!
And they show such garbage!

747
01:27:59,149 --> 01:28:01,219
I would give them an interview!

748
01:28:01,469 --> 01:28:03,982
The media is shit in this country!

749
01:28:04,148 --> 01:28:06,059
You are right.

750
01:28:06,548 --> 01:28:08,584
The keys...

751
01:28:09,148 --> 01:28:13,539
Anyway...Do you know why
Benigno is in prison?

752
01:28:13,988 --> 01:28:18,105
He is very quiet. He didn't say
a word last time he came.

753
01:28:18,667 --> 01:28:21,625
-Benigno is innocent.
-Yes, I know.

754
01:28:21,867 --> 01:28:24,779
-Innocent about what?
-I don't know.

755
01:28:25,147 --> 01:28:28,263
You do, but you don't want
to tell me.

756
01:28:33,226 --> 01:28:36,615
If you need something,
you know where I am.

757
01:30:30,215 --> 01:30:34,003
I was glad you stepped in
by yourself today, without crutches.

758
01:30:36,454 --> 01:30:39,214
-How did the exercise go today?
-Very well.

759
01:30:39,214 --> 01:30:41,374
-Were you tired?
-A lot.

760
01:30:41,374 --> 01:30:44,844
It doesn't matter. We will
do some extra exercises.

761
01:30:46,093 --> 01:30:48,766
We will do some stretches.

762
01:30:49,093 --> 01:30:52,768
-But I already did 100.
-We'll do a few more.

763
01:31:28,330 --> 01:31:31,002
I have an appointment with
Mr. Sainz.

764
01:31:35,329 --> 01:31:38,162
The boy was born dead.

765
01:31:38,289 --> 01:31:41,368
Alicia recovered.
Benigno hasn't found out.

766
01:31:41,368 --> 01:31:44,599
In his condition,
he could do something crazy.

767
01:31:45,008 --> 01:31:48,683
I can't lie to him.
He is my only friend.

768
01:31:49,168 --> 01:31:52,607
I will tell him.
I have no problem.

769
01:31:52,607 --> 01:31:56,156
Alicia is still in coma and
the baby dead, I will say.

770
01:31:56,327 --> 01:31:59,167
But you don't tell him anything.

771
01:31:59,167 --> 01:32:03,762
-Can he bail out?
-Very difficult, and expensive.

772
01:32:31,284 --> 01:32:33,963
-You are wet.
-A little.

773
01:32:33,963 --> 01:32:38,639
Be careful not to catch a cold.
Drink hot milk with honey.

774
01:32:49,802 --> 01:32:53,590
Since I am here,
I like rainy days.

775
01:32:56,081 --> 01:32:58,641
DId you see the new lawyer?

776
01:33:01,401 --> 01:33:05,360
He was here...
he told me everything...

777
01:33:07,680 --> 01:33:11,320
-I will loose, right?
-Frankly, yes, you will.

778
01:33:11,320 --> 01:33:14,756
At least nothing happened to
Alicia during birth.

779
01:33:15,160 --> 01:33:19,311
It's the only thing that consoles
me and gives me hope.

780
01:33:21,039 --> 01:33:23,234
Are you ok, Benigno?

781
01:33:26,999 --> 01:33:30,468
I would like to hug you
so much, Marco.

782
01:33:31,918 --> 01:33:35,478
But I have to ask for a meeting
face to face.

783
01:33:35,478 --> 01:33:37,514
I tried.

784
01:33:38,997 --> 01:33:41,955
They asked me whether you are
my lover.

785
01:33:42,117 --> 01:33:46,156
I didn't dare say 'yes' since
that would annoy you.

786
01:33:46,397 --> 01:33:50,708
It wouldn't annoy me at all.
You can say whatever you want.

787
01:33:51,036 --> 01:33:54,506
I have hugged very few people
in my life.

788
01:34:47,592 --> 01:34:49,423
Message!

789
01:34:53,391 --> 01:34:57,145
I was very happy to see you
and say goodbye today.

790
01:34:57,991 --> 01:35:00,551
They won't let me get
out of here...

791
01:35:00,551 --> 01:35:03,463
...or they will put me
somewhere else

792
01:35:03,751 --> 01:35:06,390
I don't want to live
without Alicia...

793
01:35:06,380 --> 01:35:10,009
...without being able to hold
not one pin of hers.

794
01:35:10,620 --> 01:35:12,929
Therefore I will escape.

795
01:35:13,220 --> 01:35:16,928
I didn't tell you so that you
won't stop me.

796
01:35:17,099 --> 01:35:19,613
I hug you firmly, Marco.

797
01:35:36,737 --> 01:35:39,649
In Zegovia...
Yes, in prison...

798
01:35:58,935 --> 01:36:02,245
I urgently need to see Benigno Martin.

799
01:36:02,535 --> 01:36:05,493
It's a matter of life and death.

800
01:36:05,775 --> 01:36:08,814
The warden is waiting for you
in his office.

801
01:36:08,814 --> 01:36:11,408
Me? Where is his office?

802
01:36:11,854 --> 01:36:14,368
The guard will accompany you.

803
01:36:21,453 --> 01:36:24,013
Empty your pockets, please.

804
01:36:37,092 --> 01:36:39,401
Wait, don't run.

805
01:36:45,331 --> 01:36:47,242
In there at the end.

806
01:36:48,691 --> 01:36:51,762
Good morning. I am
Marco Zuloaga.

807
01:36:52,410 --> 01:36:55,686
Benigno Martin left this
letter for you.

808
01:37:02,889 --> 01:37:05,089
Dear Marco...

809
01:37:05,089 --> 01:37:09,048
It's still raining, and this
is a good sign.

810
01:37:10,369 --> 01:37:13,917
When Alicia had the accident,
it was raining too.

811
01:37:14,408 --> 01:37:18,088
I am writing to you a few
minutes before I escape.

812
01:37:18,088 --> 01:37:21,608
I hope, with all these,
to fall in a coma as well...

813
01:37:21,608 --> 01:37:23,803
...and to be near her.

814
01:37:24,527 --> 01:37:26,995
You are my only friend.

815
01:37:27,447 --> 01:37:31,235
I am leaving you the house
I prepared for me and her.

816
01:37:33,087 --> 01:37:37,398
Wherever they take me, come to
see me and talk to me.

817
01:37:37,966 --> 01:37:41,675
Tell me everything, without
hiding anything.

818
01:37:42,486 --> 01:37:44,681
Goodbye, my friend.

819
01:38:01,884 --> 01:38:05,638
I took these from him and these
I found at his cell.

820
01:38:14,203 --> 01:38:16,478
You must sign here.

821
01:38:25,522 --> 01:38:27,638
Benigno, it's me.

822
01:38:30,081 --> 01:38:34,438
Alicia is alive...
You woke her up.

823
01:38:38,041 --> 01:38:42,192
I got your message and ran
immediately to tell you...

824
01:38:42,440 --> 01:38:44,874
...but it was too late.

825
01:38:45,000 --> 01:38:48,436
I put a pin of Alicia
in your pocket.

826
01:38:50,399 --> 01:38:52,959
And a photo of hers.

827
01:38:53,719 --> 01:38:56,711
And a photo of your mother.

828
01:38:57,559 --> 01:39:00,835
So that they can be with you
in eternity.

829
01:40:22,471 --> 01:40:26,100
Like wild waves. The male on top,
the female below.

830
01:40:26,391 --> 01:40:28,062
I will bring some water.

831
01:40:56,188 --> 01:40:58,099
Are you ok?

832
01:41:00,947 --> 01:41:02,903
I don't know...

833
01:41:05,307 --> 01:41:07,662
I am much better now.

834
01:41:20,426 --> 01:41:22,859
Come on, lets go inside.

835
01:41:27,865 --> 01:41:29,856
You tremble.

836
01:41:31,465 --> 01:41:32,943
Why?

837
01:41:43,863 --> 01:41:46,223
-What did you tell her?
-Noting.

838
01:41:46,223 --> 01:41:48,223
I saw you talking.

839
01:41:48,223 --> 01:41:51,579
She asked if I am ok, and I
thanked her.

840
01:41:53,422 --> 01:41:57,859
You will see me around.
I live near the dancing school.

841
01:41:58,582 --> 01:42:01,415
In Benigno's place?

842
01:42:02,022 --> 01:42:05,411
-Why do you stay there?
-Benigno is dead.

843
01:42:10,461 --> 01:42:13,612
One day, we should talk.

844
01:42:13,941 --> 01:42:17,376
Yes, and it will be simpler
than you thought.

845
01:42:17,700 --> 01:42:19,691
Nothing is simple.

846
01:42:20,100 --> 01:42:23,172
I am a dancing teacher, and nothing is simple.
and nothing is simple.

